title: Kiwi-Spiced Chicken & Veggie Toss with Hollandaise & Toasted Almonds
description: Spice it up, tonight's chicken is getting a hearty coating of our new Kiwi taste-tastic spice blend, bursting with specially crafted flavours we know you'll love. Roast the veggies and serve this meal with a drizzle of creamy hollandaise for a delicious kick.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
